Package: ggposter
Title: Build A1 Conference Posters from ggplot2 with YAML and patchwork
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R:
    person("Toshikazu", "Matsumura", , "matutosi@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: ggposter declares a poster as a title band plus columns of
    rounded, tab-headed cards (text, tables, ggplot2 figures, or photo
    strips), assembled with patchwork and rendered at true size (e.g. A1)
    with embedded fonts, including CJK. Content and layout can be described
    as an R list or a YAML file, while figures, tables, and photos are
    supplied as R objects.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://matutosi.github.io/ggposter/, https://github.com/matutosi/ggposter
BugReports: https://github.com/matutosi/ggposter/issues
